    <string name="manual_how_to">Manual / How To</string>
    <string name="manual_content">Voice Commands Guide:\n\n
1. Start Tracking a Task:\n
   • Say \"Start tracking [task name]\" or \"Begin tracking [task name]\"\n
   • Example: \"Start tracking coding\" or \"Begin tracking meeting\"\n
   • This will start timing your specified task\n\n
2. Stop Tracking:\n
   • Say \"Stop tracking\", \"End tracking\", or \"I\'m done\"\n
   • This will stop timing your current task\n\n
3. Break Management:\n
   • Start Break: Say \"Take a break\" or \"Start break\"\n
   • End Break: Say \"Stop break\" or \"Back to work\"\n\n
4. Navigation Commands:\n
   • Show Export Page: \"Show export\" or \"Export data\"\n
   • Show Manual: \"Show manual\" or \"Show help\"\n
   • Show Timesheet: \"Show timesheet\" or \"View my hours\"\n
   • Show Statistics: \"Show statistics\" or \"Show stats\"\n\n
5. Task Management:\n
   • Delete Task: \"Delete task [task name]\" or \"Remove task [task name]\"\n\n
Note: The app recognizes various similar phrases for each command. Feel free to speak naturally!</string>
    
